  <brief_title>Study to Assess Safety &amp; Tolerability of AZD2281 in Combination With Bevacizumab in Patients With Advanced Solid Tumours</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Open Label, Dual Centre Study To Assess The Safety And Tolerability Of AZD2281 In Combination With Bevacizumab (AvastinÂ®) In Patients With Advanced Solid Tumours</official_title>
  <sponsors>
