  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Phase I, open label, dual centre, dose finding study to evaluate the safety and tolerability
      of continuous twice daily oral dosing with AZD2281 when administered in combination with
      Bevacizumab 10mg/kg given every 2 weeks to patients with advanced solid tumours.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
